snippet.title: Celestial Empire - Official Trailer | New City-Building Game
snippet.description:
A brand new trailer presents the implementation of the latest technologies in a city-builder. Recorded all in-game, with special attention paid to the stunning details achieved thanks to UE5’s Nanite Geometry System.
Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1330430/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/CelestialEmpr 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/CelestialEmpireTheGame 
Website: https://president-studio.com

#indiedev #UE5 #trailer
